(11, 'company_welcome', 'The Big Bearing Store was started in 2005 after we noticed that there was a real lack of quality bearing and power transmission suppliers on the internet. Coming from the wholesale side of the bearing industry, we brought with us the idea of passing on the savings that come from buying direct from the factories.', '', ''),
