(76, 'Muhamad Rizki Akbar', '', 'mrizkiakbar24@gmail.com', '', '', '', 'Dear Filantropi Indonesia,\n\nI am writing to asking about job oppourtunity in Filantropi Indonesia. I have recently graduated with a degree in communication science at the University of Brawijaya. \n\nHaving the professional experience in producing events, social programs, public relations, media monitoring, negotiations and also academic experience in marketing communication, I have undertaken an internship for UNDP and KEHATI foundation. I have also worked as an event organizer and I have joined a traninner organization for trained students in developing their leadership skills. Futhermore, I also have an experience be a research assistant in communication science for 1 years. I am multi-skilled, therefore, handling multiple tasks at one period of time would not be an issue at all. \n \nI am very interested in joining your team in Filantropi Indonesia because I believe I can offer my skills to help develop Filantropi Indonesia  For further questions, please feel free to contact me on 081298073772. Thank you for your time. I look forward to hearing from you soon.\n \nSincerely,', 'R', '2018-12-09 15:10:46', ''),
