(130, 'Rika Ariska', '', 'rikaariska7784@gmail.com', '', '', '', 'Selamat pagi, saya ingin menanyakan terkait lowongan kerja sebagai staff vokasi di Yayasan Adaro Bangun Negeri. saya sudah 2 kali kirim email lamaran namun selalu tertolak karena mailbox penuh. Kira-kira ada link lain untuk melamar pekerjaan tersebut? terimakasih', 'U', '2019-08-29 02:41:35', ''),
(131, 'Patricia', '', 'patriciacalvovillalobos@hotmail.com', '', '', '', 'Good Morning, My Name is Patricia Calvo I live in Cartagena,colombia.\n I have a small foundation that is dedicated to children\'s mental health and to give neuroeducational programs to enhance the cognitive areas of children in learning, also the care of the environment and the area Food and recreation.\nThe foundation is called the Bindu Seed Foundation on Facebook. We appear as the Bindu Fund seed, we would like to know how you could help us get funds for the programs we want to make for the benefit of children and young people in Turbaco, Bolivar.\nI thank you for the attention you can give to my request.\nSincerely\nPatricia Calvo\nBindu Seed Foundation Director\nTurbaco, Bolivar, Colombia\ncel: 3215972514', 'U', '2019-09-03 16:50:00', ''),
