(148, 'Philanthropy Learning Forum 11', '', 'PLF ke-11 akan dilaksanakan dengan tema Cause-related Marketing pada 17 November 2016', '<h3 style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/pubs/uploads/images/PLF%2011%20CRM.png\" style=\"height:343px; width:721px\" /></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cause-Related Marketing (CRM) merupakan salah satu cara perusahaan dan konsumen untuk menunjukkan kepedulian dan kontribusinya terhadap persoalan tertentu yang terjadi di masyarakat melalui perangkat, skema dan saluran pemasaran yang dimiliki perusahaan. Selain penyisihan keuntungan melalui pembelian produk tertentu, CRM juga dilakukan melalui skema <em>buy one give one</em>, pembulatan transaksi, <em>change for good</em> dan lain-lain. Dalam prakteknya, skema kembalian ini kemudian banyak digunakan untuk menggalang kepedulian masyarakat oleh pengelola supermarket dan toko swalayan.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harus diakui bahwa kegiatan CRM merupakan strategi yang mudah dilakukan dan banyak membantu lembaga-lembaga sosial dalam menggalang donasi masyarakat lewat bantuan perusahaan. Di sisi lain, CRM juga bisa menjadi strategi pemasaran efektif bagi perusahaan dalam meningkatkan penjualan dan citra produk maupun perusahaannya.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Namun, dalam beberapa bulan terakhir, praktek CRM banyak dipersoalkan seiring dengan maraknya pengaduan dari pelanggan mengenai praktik CRM yang dianggap kurang tepat, tidak etis dan transparan. Jika persoalan ini tidak dicarikan solusi dan dibiarkan berlarut-larut, maka dikhawatirkan bisa mereduksi kegiatan filantropi yang dilakukan oleh perusahaan maupun konsumen.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Untuk mengoptimalkan peran dan kontribusi CRM dalam kegiatan filantropi di Indonesia, <strong>Filantropi Indonesia </strong>bekerja sama dengan<strong> Dompet Dhuafa </strong>mengadakan <strong><em>Philanthropy Learning Forum </em></strong><strong>ke-11</strong> dengan tema <strong>&ldquo;</strong><strong><em>Cause Related Marketing: Peran dan Problematikanya dalam Pengembangan Filantropi</em></strong><strong><em>&rdquo;</em></strong> yang akan diselenggarakan pada<strong> Kamis</strong><strong>, </strong><strong>17 November </strong><strong>&nbsp;2016</strong>.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Undangan untuk kalangan terbatas, silakan kontak informasi@filantropi-indonesia.org untuk informasi lebih lanjut.</p>\n', '8ce5c012184ca8d99429061ac1e25967.jpg', '', 0, 'Y', 'P', '2016-10-14 07:02:25', '2016-11-11 16:23:28', 5, 'philanthropy-learning-forum-11', 'events', 0, '', 'id', '', '', '', '', '', 'zTFUN2P9qYIBUMo', 'N', '', '', '2016-11-17 00:00:00', '2016-11-17 23:59:59'),
(149, 'Philanthropy Learning Forum 11', '', 'The 11th PLF will be held with the theme Cause-related Marketing on November 17, 2016', '<h3 style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/pubs/uploads/images/PLF%2011%20CRM%281%29.png\" style=\"height:343px; width:721px\" /></h3>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cause-Related Marketing (CRM) is a tool for companies and consumers who wants to contribute to solve certain problems in the community through marketing strategy by enterprises. CRM is usually done by allocating a small amount of profit through the purchase of a particular product, buy one give one, rounding up the total of transactions, etc. The rounding up or donating your small change scheme is then used to raise public awareness by most supermarkets and convenience stores.<br />\n<br />\nIt should be known that CRM is a strategy that is easy to do and has helped many nonprofits in the community to raise donations through partnership with companies. On the other hand, CRM also can be an effective marketing strategy for the company to increase sales and create a positive image of the product or the company.<br />\n<br />\nHowever, in recent months, many CRM practices are in question with increasing complaints from customers about the practice of CRM that&#39;s considered improper, unethical and not transparent. If the issue is not resolved and no solution is found soon, then it could reduce philanthropic activities by companies and consumers.<br />\n<br />\nTo optimize the role and contribution of CRM to philanthropy activities in Indonesia, <strong>Indonesia Philanthropy Association </strong>in partnership with <strong>Dompet Dhuafa</strong> will hole the 11th Philanthropy Learning Forum with the theme <strong>&quot;Cause Related Marketing: Its Role and Problems in the Development of Philanthropy&quot;</strong> which will be held on <strong>Thursday, November 17, 2016</strong>.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Invitation only, please e-mail us at informasi@filantropi-indonesia.org for more details.</p>\n', '8ce5c012184ca8d99429061ac1e25967.jpg', '', 0, 'Y', 'P', '2016-10-14 07:02:25', '2016-11-11 16:23:28', 5, 'philanthropy-learning-forum-11', 'events', 0, '', 'en', '', '', '', '', '', 'zTFUN2P9qYIBUMo', 'N', '', '', '2016-11-17 00:00:00', '2016-11-17 23:59:59'),
(150, 'Global Summit on Community Philanthropy', '', '', '<p><strong>Global Summit on Community Philanthropy - 1-2 December 2016, Johannesberg, South Africa.</strong></p>\n\n<p>The summit offers a unique opportunity to engage with a broad range of actors linked to the community philanthropy field.&nbsp;</p>\n', '8a4b3be5663ce34ce6ccdc323411c781.jpeg', '', 0, 'Y', 'P', '2016-10-14 07:08:25', '2016-10-21 10:35:25', 5, 'global-summit-on-community-philanthropy', 'events', 0, '', 'id', '', '', '', '', '', 'qWpvph84BcrUbER', 'N', '', '', '2016-12-01 00:00:00', '2016-12-02 23:59:59'),
