(330, 'Young Social Innovator Competition', '', 'Kitabisa.com in collaboration with Filantropi Indonesia organized a Young Social Innovator Competition program, a competition for young people under the age of 30 to create social innovation.', '<p>The Indonesia Philanthropy Festival (IPFest) 2016 was the first ever Philanthropy Festival in Indonesia. The festival had the following aims:</p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li>Introduce to the community the development and progress of philanthropy and its contribution to the achievement of Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs).</li>\n	<li>Increase the understanding and capacity of philanthropic activists about the latest opportunities and challenges that affect the effectiveness of philanthropy in Indonesia.</li>\n	<li>Increase the understanding of philanthropic stakeholders on Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) as well as encourage the effectiveness of the implementation of Philanthropy Platform SDGs.</li>\n	<li>Fostering and facilitating synergy and partnerships between philanthropic actors and philanthropic actors with program implementing organizations, especially in achieving the target of SDGs.</li>\n	<li>Increase the real contribution of Indonesian philanthropy in various efforts to realize the welfare of society and social justice.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>At the festival, Kitabisa.com collaborated with Filantropi Indonesia to hold a Young Social Innovator Competition program, which is a competition for those under the age of 30 who are actively engaged in projects involving social innovation. Some examples of project areas included mobile applications, technology for the poor, products and services for the poor, to common social initiatives still under the umbrella of Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs). The best, most innovative ideas that are chosen as winners will get both technical and financial support to further their projects. With this partnership, IPFest 2016 wants to give support to young people who are raising money, through kitabisa or otherwise, for the development of their social enterprise. The following is a list of participants:</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:690px\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:57px\">\n			<p><strong>No</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:239px\">\n			<p><strong>Innovation</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:129px\">\n			<p><strong>Summary</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:137px\">\n			<p><strong>Presentation</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:127px\">\n			<p><strong>Video</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:57px\">\n			<p><strong>1</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:239px\">\n			<p>1000Guru</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:129px\">\n			<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B7t4yaZkU37pMWRLTkgwdGpnOWs/view?usp=sharing\">Link</a></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:137px\">\n			<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B7t4yaZkU37pdEJLUWRmWGFYS3M/view?usp=sharing\">Link</a></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:127px\">\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:57px\">\n			<p><strong>2</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:239px\">\n			<p>Agroinvestasi</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:129px\">\n			<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B7t4yaZkU37pMWRLTkgwdGpnOWs/view?usp=sharing\">Link</a></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:137px\">\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:127px\">\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:57px\">\n			<p><strong>3</strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:239px\">\n			<p>Angkring</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"height:19px; width:129px\">\n			<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B7t4